{
  "message": "chore: bump Browser Edition packages and docs from 0.2.7 to 0.2.8\n\nBumps version strings across all Browser Edition npm packages\n(@asupersync/browser-core, @asupersync/browser, @asupersync/next,\n@asupersync/react) from 0.2.7 to 0.2.8.\n\nUpdates all documentation references to the minimum asupersync version:\n- tokio_external_validation_benchmark_packs.md: evidence pack version\n- tokio_fs_process_signal_migration_playbook.md: Cargo.toml minimum\n- tokio_t6_migration_packs.md: Cargo.toml minimum\n- wasm_artifact_strategy.md: dependency version in example Cargo.toml\n\nRefreshes WASM supply-chain integrity artifacts to match the new\npackage.json SHA-256 digests:\n- wasm_browser_artifact_integrity_manifest_v1.json: updated hashes for\n  browser-core, browser, react, next package.json and for the sbom and\n  provenance attestation files themselves\n- wasm_browser_provenance_attestation_v1.json: updated attestation\n  metadata for 0.2.8\n- wasm_browser_sbom_v1.json: updated SBOM entries for 0.2.8\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
